---
title: Quick Almond & Garlic Hasselback Chicken with Lemon Crushed Potatoes & Cucumber Salad
description: We've put all the much-loved flavour combos into this delectable dinner – from the almond and garlic-crusted
chicken breast to the lemony crushed potatoes – it's got everything we're all addicted to!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-almond-garlic-crusted-chicken-c059c3c4.jpg
